{"tid":1676785,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"(PC) [二戰Flight Sim] IL-2 Sturmovik討論區 「Steam 25折」","createTime":"2019-10-26T16:21:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T05:55:32.000Z","uid":82520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a72a975dc9bee95835388e2fd7f8c0ac601d17b2","tid":1676785,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgur.com/MkL56Wa\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FMkL56Wa&h=f1815689&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e4aGYa7QdAQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3De4aGYa7QdAQ&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjgx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=9c657893\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e4aGYa7QdAQ</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/307960/IL2_Sturmovik_Battle_of_Stalingrad/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F307960%2FIL2_Sturmovik_Battle_of_Stalingrad%2F&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjgx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=820245ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/307960/IL2_Sturmovik_Battle_of_Stalingrad/</a><br />\nIL-2 係好多年嘅二戰Flight Sim ip，而IL-2 Sturmovik 就係佢地嘅最新作<br />\n當中有唔同戰役要分開買，每個戰役可以當係大型dlc有8-10架飛機＋單機任務<br />\n當中分為：<br />\nBattle of Stalingrad<br />\nBattle of Moscow<br />\nBattle of Kuban<br />\nBattle of Bodenplatte<br />\n新手多數推薦買Battle of Stalingrad，因為係steam要買左BOS先可以買其他戰役。<br />\n係官網買就冇呢個限制，邊個戰役都可以單獨買。<br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝硬件要求＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n咁玩呢個game有咩要求？其實用鍵鼠都得不過你會痛不欲生。<br />\n所以都係推薦要有HOTAS／joystick<br />\n最平可以買logitech，中階可以買thrustmaster嘅t16000m，最高階可以考慮VKB/Virpil等。<br />\n不過有樣比HOTAS更重要係頭瞄，姐係head tracking。<br />\nVR headset係其中一種，不過flight sim用嘅最出名都係TrackIR5，嫌貴淘寶有老番。<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>重點係咩？重點係依加賣緊25折咋</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/307960/IL2_Sturmovik_Battle_of_Stalingrad/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F307960%2FIL2_Sturmovik_Battle_of_Stalingrad%2F&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjgx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=820245ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/307960/IL2_Sturmovik_Battle_of_Stalingrad/</a><br />\n覺得難入手嘅唔緊要，買左之後手把手教你都得<br />\ngear呢啲搵下二手慢慢買就得<br />\n<br />\n講咁多其實都係想有人一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一真都搵唔到香港人wingman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b1492631018bf14a6e576c1f8d967e1aceaf4a1","tid":1676785,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:21:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c563f8eecdda690292bec7856fa1288fb4df6e90","tid":1676785,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:21:27.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"080e20995c7f977bdb54d182d5fcf7028a6aef6d","tid":1676785,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:22:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MkL56Wa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMkL56Wa.png&h=fb28660b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6079f776b3a64cf3b0b1127c4f15766a567800a0","tid":1676785,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steamcommunity/public/images/clans/6585301/62f6ff04eb3ef88080e4868a316a86e7a7839ab0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamcdn-a.akamaihd.net%2Fsteamcommunity%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fclans%2F6585301%2F62f6ff04eb3ef88080e4868a316a86e7a7839ab0.jpg&h=98bd9f93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https:/